Jobs in Indus Valley School of Art / Architecture
Karachi
IVS is a not-for-profit, Higher Education, Degree-Awarding Institution, providing a comprehensive education in Art & Design, based on rigorous studio practice as well as in-depth academic study. IVS invites applications from eligible candidates for the following posts:
Coordinator - Department of Interior Design
A strong background of Interior Design work along with sound administrative skills are required.
Permanent & Adjunct Faculty Positions in:
- Department of Architecture
- Department of Interior Design
- Department of Communication Design
- Liberal Arts Programme
A minimum of 16 years of higher education (either a 4-year internationally recognized Bachelor's degree or a Pakistani University MA.) in the relevant field is mandatory.
Administrative Officer
Graduate degree with 2-5 years work experience in administration is mandatory. Candidates must have own motorcycle.
The job description of advertised positions are available on our website: www.indusvalley.edu.pk/jobs.html
Applications to be submitted electronically at: hr@indusvalley.edu.pk
Indus Valley School of Art and Architecture,
ST-33, Block-2, Scheme-5, Clifton, Karachi-75600 UAN: 111-111-487 Fax: 021-35861048
